Brown sausage in 12-inch nonstick skillet over medium-high heat, about 5 minutes. Remove sausage from skillet and set aside. Heat olive oil in same skillet over medium-high heat and cook green peppers, onion and garlic, stirring occasionally, 5 minutes or until vegetables are tender. Stir in Pasta Sauce and bring to a boil. Return sausage to skillet. Reduce heat to low and simmer covered, stirring occasionally, 10 minutes or until sausage is done and vegetables are tender. Serve, if desired, with crusty Italian bread.